          "description": {
            "_cdata": "<p>DLsite公開最新中文語系特別活動：「DLsite 秋の回憶 特惠活動」，除了介紹中文矚目新作外，也提供特別回饋優惠券、中文同捆購買特惠等活動。</p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/30850\">「DLsite 秋の回憶 特惠活動」進行中 推出特別回饋優惠券、中文同捆購買特惠等</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
          "content:encoded": {
            "_cdata": "\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">DLsite公開最新中文語系特別活動：「DLsite 秋の回憶 特惠活動」，除了介紹中文矚目新作外，也提供特別回饋優惠券、中文同捆購買特惠等活動。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"553\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11010424/202411singlesdaytw01-1024x553.webp\" alt=\"202411singlesdaytw01\" class=\"wp-image-30851\" title=\"「DLsite 秋の回憶 特惠活動」進行中 推出特別回饋優惠券、中文同捆購買特惠等 1\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11010424/202411singlesdaytw01-1024x553.webp 1024w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11010424/202411singlesdaytw01-300x162.webp 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11010424/202411singlesdaytw01-768x415.webp 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11010424/202411singlesdaytw01-750x405.webp 750w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11010424/202411singlesdaytw01-1140x616.webp 1140w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11010424/202411singlesdaytw01.webp 1478w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">特別回饋優惠券包含提供給新會員，可用於所有作品的300円優惠券；還有根據用戶的使用情況，提供的「感謝與回饋」優惠券。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"857\" height=\"845\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11010428/202411singlesdaytw02.webp\" alt=\"202411singlesdaytw02\" class=\"wp-image-30852\" title=\"「DLsite 秋の回憶 特惠活動」進行中 推出特別回饋優惠券、中文同捆購買特惠等 2\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11010428/202411singlesdaytw02.webp 857w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11010428/202411singlesdaytw02-300x296.webp 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11010428/202411singlesdaytw02-768x757.webp 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11010428/202411singlesdaytw02-75x75.webp 75w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11010428/202411singlesdaytw02-750x739.webp 750w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 857px) 100vw, 857px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">大家一起來翻譯則是提供最多7.5折的優惠券。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"669\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11010432/202411singlesdaytw03-1024x669.webp\" alt=\"202411singlesdaytw03\" class=\"wp-image-30853\" title=\"「DLsite 秋の回憶 特惠活動」進行中 推出特別回饋優惠券、中文同捆購買特惠等 3\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11010432/202411singlesdaytw03-1024x669.webp 1024w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11010432/202411singlesdaytw03-300x196.webp 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11010432/202411singlesdaytw03-768x502.webp 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11010432/202411singlesdaytw03-750x490.webp 750w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11010432/202411singlesdaytw03-1140x745.webp 1140w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11010432/202411singlesdaytw03.webp 1230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">另外中文矚目新作，則是有模擬類遊戲<a href=\"https://www.dlsite.com/maniax/dlaf/=/t/s/link/work/aid/moelong2307/locale/zh_TW/id/RJ01189784.html/?locale=zh_TW\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.dlsite.com/maniax/dlaf/=/t/s/link/work/aid/moelong2307/locale/zh_TW/id/RJ01189784.html/?locale=zh_TW\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">《Sisters Connect 想要訴説的心意》</a>。</p>\n\n\n\n<a rel=\"noopener sponsored\" href=\"https://www.dlsite.com/maniax/dlaf/=/t/i/link/work/aid/moelong2307/locale/zh_TW/id/RJ01189784.html/?locale=zh_TW\" target=\"_blank\"><img decoding=\"async\" itemprop=\"image\" src=\"//img.dlsite.jp/modpub/images2/work/doujin/RJ01190000/RJ01189784_img_main.jpg\" alt=\"RJ01189784 img main\" border=\"0\" class=\"target_type\" title=\"「DLsite 秋の回憶 特惠活動」進行中 推出特別回饋優惠券、中文同捆購買特惠等 4\"></a>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">與ASMR<a href=\"https://www.dlsite.com/maniax/dlaf/=/t/s/link/work/aid/moelong2307/locale/zh_TW/id/RJ01255809.html/?locale=zh_TW\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.dlsite.com/maniax/dlaf/=/t/s/link/work/aid/moelong2307/locale/zh_TW/id/RJ01255809.html/?locale=zh_TW\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">《與悠姊姊在圖書館的秘密自習課》</a>。</p>\n\n\n\n<a rel=\"noopener sponsored\" href=\"https://www.dlsite.com/maniax/dlaf/=/t/i/link/work/aid/moelong2307/locale/zh_TW/id/RJ01255809.html/?locale=zh_TW\" target=\"_blank\"><img decoding=\"async\" itemprop=\"image\" src=\"//img.dlsite.jp/modpub/images2/work/doujin/RJ01256000/RJ01255809_img_main.jpg\" alt=\"RJ01255809 img main\" border=\"0\" class=\"target_type\" title=\"「DLsite 秋の回憶 特惠活動」進行中 推出特別回饋優惠券、中文同捆購買特惠等 5\"></a>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">中文同捆購買特惠，在<a href=\"https://www.dlsite.com/pro/dlaf/=/aid/moelong2307/url/https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dlsite.com%2Fpro%2Fcampaign%2Fbulkbuy%2F%3D%2Fkey%2Fzh202411%2F%3Futm_medium%3Daffiliate%26utm_campaign%3Dbnlink%26utm_content%3Dtext\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.dlsite.com/pro/dlaf/=/aid/moelong2307/url/https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dlsite.com%2Fpro%2Fcampaign%2Fbulkbuy%2F%3D%2Fkey%2Fzh202411%2F%3Futm_medium%3Daffiliate%26utm_campaign%3Dbnlink%26utm_content%3Dtext\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">指定頁面</a>中同時購買3部活動作品，享最高5折折扣。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"716\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11010436/202411singlesdaytw04-1024x716.webp\" alt=\"202411singlesdaytw04\" class=\"wp-image-30854\" title=\"「DLsite 秋の回憶 特惠活動」進行中 推出特別回饋優惠券、中文同捆購買特惠等 6\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11010436/202411singlesdaytw04-1024x716.webp 1024w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11010436/202411singlesdaytw04-300x210.webp 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11010436/202411singlesdaytw04-768x537.webp 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11010436/202411singlesdaytw04-750x524.webp 750w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11010436/202411singlesdaytw04-1140x797.webp 1140w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11010436/202411singlesdaytw04.webp 1236w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">「DLsite 秋の回憶 特惠活動」至2024年11月13日22：59分(台灣時間)</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"https://tongren.jp/lp/maniax/singlesday202411/tw/\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://tongren.jp/lp/maniax/singlesday202411/tw/\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"> 「DLsite 秋の回憶 特惠活動」活動頁面</a></p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/30850\">「DLsite 秋の回憶 特惠活動」進行中 推出特別回饋優惠券、中文同捆購買特惠等</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
